<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Recuperação de Senha</title>
  <style>
    @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Sora:wght@300;400;600;700&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;700&display=swap');
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    body { background-color: #0d0f14; font-family: 'Sora', sans-serif; color: #e2e8f0; padding: 40px 16px; }
    .wrapper { max-width: 560px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 32px; }
    .logo { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; }
    .logo-icon { width: 36px; height: 36px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6366f1, #a855f7); border-radius: 10px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; }
    .logo-text { font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700; color: #f1f5f9; }
    .card { background: #161a24; border: 1px solid #1e2535; border-radius: 20px; overflow: hidden; }
    .card-banner { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1033 0%, #0f172a 50%, #1a1033 100%); padding: 48px 40px 36px; text-align: center; }
    .lock-icon { width: 64px; height: 64px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6366f1, #a855f7); border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; margin: 0 auto 0; font-size: 28px; }
    .card-banner h1 { font-size: 22px; font-weight: 700; color: #f8fafc; margin-bottom: 8px; }
    .card-banner p { font-size: 14px; color: #94a3b8; font-weight: 300; line-height: 1.6; }
    .card-banner strong { color: #c4b5fd; font-weight: 600; }
    .card-body { padding: 36px 40px 40px; }
    .instruction { font-size: 13px; color: #64748b; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1.2px; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 14px; }
    .code-box { background: #0d0f14; border: 1px solid #2d3748; border-radius: 14px; padding: 28px; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 28px; }
    .code-label { font-size: 11px; color: #475569; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1.5px; margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .code-value { font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 38px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 12px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #818cf8, #c084fc); -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent; background-clip: text; }
    .code-expiry { margin-top: 14px; font-size: 12px; color: #475569; }
    .dot { width: 6px; height: 6px; background: #f59e0b; border-radius: 50%; display: inline-block; margin-right: 6px; }
    .security-notice { background: rgba(245,158,11,0.06); border: 1px solid rgba(245,158,11,0.15); border-radius: 10px; padding: 14px 16px; display: flex; gap: 12px; margin-bottom: 28px; }
    .notice-text { font-size: 12.5px; color: #94a3b8; line-height: 1.6; }
    .notice-text strong { color: #fbbf24; font-weight: 600; }
    .divider { height: 1px; background: linear-gradient(to right, transparent, #1e2535, transparent); margin: 28px 0; }
    .ignore-text { font-size: 12.5px; color: #475569; text-align: center; line-height: 1.7; }
    .footer { text-align: center; margin-top: 28px; }
    .footer p { font-size: 11.5px; color: #334155; line-height: 1.8; }
    .footer a { color: #6366f1; text-decoration: none; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrapper">
    <div class="header">
      <div class="logo">
        <div class="logo-icon">
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none">
            <path d="M12 2L2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5zM2 17l10 5 10-5M2 12l10 5 10-5" stroke="white" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <span class="logo-text">PanMetrics</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-banner">
        <div class="lock-icon">🔐</div>
        <h1>Recuperação de senha</h1>
        <p>Olá, <strong>{{name}}</strong>! Recebemos uma solicitação<br/>para redefinir sua senha.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="card-body">
        <p class="instruction">Seu código de verificação</p>

        <div class="code-box">
          <p class="code-label">Use este código para continuar</p>
          <div class="code-value">{{code}}</div>
          <div class="code-expiry">
            <span class="dot"></span>
            Expira em <strong style="color:#fbbf24; margin-left:3px;">10 minutos</strong>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="security-notice">
          <span>⚠️</span>
          <p class="notice-text">
            <strong>Nunca compartilhe este código.</strong> Nossa equipe jamais solicitará
            seu código de verificação por telefone, chat ou e-mail.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="divider"></div>

        <p class="ignore-text">
          Se você não solicitou a recuperação de senha, ignore este e-mail.
          Sua senha permanece a mesma.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>
        &copy; {{year}} PanMetrics. Todos os direitos reservados.<br/>
        <a href="#">Política de Privacidade</a> &middot; <a href="#">Suporte</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>